headline: Tractor Supply Welcomes Lincoln Electric to Its Top-Tier Welding Lineup
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., June 03, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, is excited to welcome Lincoln Electric, the global leader in advanced welding solutions, to its lineup of premier welding brands. Tractor Supply customers can now find Lincoln Electric’s industry-renowned welders, helmets, protective gear, brushes, accessories and more at Tractor Supply stores across the country and online at TractorSupply.com.
